Our Cleaning Pipeline
stressors &lt;- stressors_messy |&gt;
  rename(state = State, varroa_mites = `Varroa mites (%)`, ...) |&gt;
  mutate(state = str_to_title(state)) |&gt;
  mutate(across(varroa_mites:unknown,
    \(x) str_replace_all(x, "\\(Z\\)", "0"))) |&gt;
  mutate(across(varroa_mites:unknown, parse_number)) |&gt;
  filter(str_detect(quarter, "2024")) |&gt;
  pivot_longer(cols = varroa_mites:unknown,
               names_to = "stressor",
               values_to = "pct_affected")
The pipe |&gt; chains each step ‚Äî readable top to bottom, like a recipe.
